# ROADMAP.md — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

> Phases are gates. Each phase ends with a `/phase-review` from `product-owner-reviewer`. Do not begin phase N+1 until phase N is signed off.

## Phase 0 — Scaffold ✅ (Completed by initial setup)

**Goal:** Get the repo, agents, hooks, and planning docs in place before writing product code.

Deliverables:
- [x] Planning docs (CLAUDE.md, PROJECT_CONTEXT.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, ROADMAP.md, SECURITY_MODEL.md, TASKS.md, DECISIONS.md, README.md, HANDOFF.md)
- [x] `.claude/` with settings, 11 subagents, 9 slash commands, hooks
- [x] Monorepo directory skeleton
- [x] (if regulated) Domain corpus seed
- [x] Makefile, docker-compose.yml, .gitignore, pre-commit
- [x] Guardrail scripts

**Exit criteria:** `git init && git commit`, then `claude` runs in this folder with all agents available.

