## Phase N — Demo polish + deployment guide

**Goal:** A demo you can show to a real user without apologies.

Deliverables:
- Seeded demo workspace
- Demo script (`docs/sales/demo-script.md`)
- Loom recording of the demo flow
- Deployment guide
- Optional: one-page sales sheet

**Exit criteria:** Fresh-laptop user follows README → has a working demo in < 30 minutes.

`/phase-review` from `product-owner-reviewer` — **this is the major-milestone mark**.

